metadata.name: Mercedes Benz SLS AMG
metadata.description:
The Mercedes Benz SLS AMG (C197 / R197) is a front mid-engine, 2-seater, limited production grand tourer developed by the Mercedes-AMG division of German automotive manufacturer Mercedes-Benz, with the assistance of David Coulthard. [Link]( https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mercedes-Benz_SLS_AMG)
